Package exp.data

MS spectrum related classes - provide feature extraction and peak pre-processing

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Fasta
    Manage database file and make decoys
    IsoCluster
    Manage Isotope cluster information
    Peak
    Store one peak information of a spectrum
    Spectra
    Read MS spectra from one or more *mgf(or *mzXML) files and store them to list
    SpectralAnalyzer
    Calculate additional features of spectra which cannot get values directly from a spectrum
    Spectrum
    Store spectrum information, extract features, and pre-process peaks
    Tag
    Calculate sequence tags among the list of given peaks
    XICPeak
    Manage XIC peaks
